dct_title_s: Automobile road map touring Los Angeles and vicinity
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; drawn by Elmer J. Brown.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways, resorts, beaches.
